            <description><![CDATA[
<h2>What's New</h2>

<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Fix Sparkle auto-update not triggering background checks for menu bar apps</li>
<li>Add comprehensive logging for update check debugging (viewable in Console.app)</li>
<li>Add "Last Checked" display in Settings to verify update checks are occurring</li>
<li>Schedule automatic background check 30 seconds after app launch</li>
</ul>

<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>Debug tool to force background update check (DEBUG builds only)</li>
</ul>

See <a href="https://github.com/tartinerlabs/ClaudeMeter/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md">CHANGELOG.md</a> for full details.
